divs: Sighting DetailsAt the exact time given, when I was walking to work down by the Deschutes River, I noticed a large white light that was traveling FROM where Venus was located southwest in a straight line towards the northeast. It traveled slow, there were NO flashing air traffic lights at all!! NO sound! I have seen the space station one time and this was similar BUT the space station had travel exactly from west to east. Could somebody verify if this was the space station? My coworker had also witnessed the same object as I did.
Summary: Large white light (no flashing lights....was this the Space Station???).
